version_description: Beautiful new song by Linkin Park. I could only find a version of this song with a Capo on the 3rd Fret so I transposed it up 3 semitones so you can play without a capo or play on a piano or another instrument easily. Hope it's all good :) #RIPCHESTER.
The ORIGINAL Chords - the other versions had all some (little) mistakes
Chords-version for playing it to accompany a voice. Added tab by biebrich at the end.
